"the team\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also marked a record medal haul for us as a team, with seven, and we secured the final three Olympic quota spots forParisthissummer.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a record medal haul\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"the final three Olympic quota spots\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"forParisthissummer\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No one is getting carried away after the team's performance in Qatar but it is more experience under my belt and I do not think you can ever have too much of that.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7169992285534612, \"rank\": 0.3947013924104384, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's performance\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"more experience\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"my belt\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone who has bundles of experience is Tom, my mixed synchro partner, who has returned to the team.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Someone\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"bundles\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"my mixed synchro partner\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is 30 this year and is so inspirational.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's nice to have him back.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His work ethic is like no one else and just being around him makes you want to work harder, but I doubt I will do what he has done and carry on diving at that stage of my life.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His work\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom has started a family and has returned with the Paris Games in mind.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, I have a love-hate relationship with the sport and when you have that, you tend to fantasise about when it will be over one day!\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a love-hate relationship\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"one day\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's just the reality of elite-level sport from an athlete's point of view.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the reality\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"elite-level sport\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's point\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"view\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to have a family too one day and be as present as possible, and I am looking forward to the day I retire.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's different as a woman and I want to settle down in the future.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have also given so much to diving.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not exactly dive when pregnant, of course, although there were women in the field in Doha who have had kids and come back and that is so inspiring.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.150845823272545e-11, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 1999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not see that being what I am going to do, though.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had my retirement plan in the back of my mind since I was 13 but we are far away from that, I am happy to say.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my retirement plan\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now I want to make history and for me that means beating the Chinese, who it's difficult not to see as perfection in my sport.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2279, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.7033444155585175, \"rank\": 0.3981704084276928, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To defeat them will be a difficult journey but not impossible.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difficult journey\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They train so much - in fact, that is all they do: train, train, train and train.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"train\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"train\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"train\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are also younger and a lot smaller than me.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been told by some people that having long legs is my superpower.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"long legs\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"my superpower\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before, it was an insecurity of mine but I have come to love and embrace my body shape.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an insecurity\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"my body shape\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe I can close that gap to the guys who beat me in Qatar - Quan Hongchan and Chen Yuxi, who won gold and silver respectively in the individual and then teamed up to claim gold in the synchro, with Mi Rae Kim and Jin Mi Jo, of North Korea, taking the silver medal.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7169992285534612, \"rank\": 0.3947013924104384, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yuxi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Yuxi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yuxi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yuxi\"}, {\"begin\": 2913, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9999986611223771, \"rank\": 1.098100349541938e-06, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 2922, \"end\": 2925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin-Soo_Kwon\", \"score\": 0.9993332728258333, \"rank\": 0.0006669164262783721, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin-Soo_Kwon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin-Soo_Kwon\"}, {\"begin\": 2929, \"end\": 2931, \"