y did not have to say yes to that.\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.7033444155585175, \"rank\": 0.3981704084276928, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a lovely gesture from them.\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lovely gesture\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know what my task is over the next five months and my goal is to cut that gap to the Chinese divers.\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3316, \"end\": 3323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.7033444155585175, \"rank\": 0.3981704084276928, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my task\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"the next five months\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"my goal\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"that gap\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's been a great start to the year and I look forward to what lies ahead.\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great start\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3359}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lotteryplayers raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sports - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"National Lotteryplayers\", \"f